{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8a1b9b00-0001-4000-8000-000000000008",
    "name": "Dumble Wallet — Real QA Suite",
    "description": "Exhaustive contract surface for Wallet. Dual-auth: /wallet/me/** + /admin/wallet/** require USER JWT (signed with JWT_SECRET); /wallet/credit + /wallet/debit + /wallet/{userId}/summary require SYSTEM JWT (signed with SERVICE_JWT_SIGNING_KEY, aud=wallet). The collection hits Wallet directly on its host port so the gateway's user-JWT filter doesn't reject system tokens, plus a few through-gateway smoke tests. Runner pre-seeds JWTs: user (alice/bob/admin/expired/no-userid/wrong-key) + system (service/admin-iss/payment-aud/no-aud/expired/wrong-key/no-exp/no-iss).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth boundary",
      "item": [
        {"name":"1.1 POST /wallet/credit no token → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-noauth-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.2 POST /wallet/credit user JWT (not system) → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-userjwt-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.3 POST /wallet/credit system JWT aud=payment → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_payment_aud}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-wrongaud-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.4 POST /wallet/credit system JWT no aud → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_no_aud}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-noaud-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.5 POST /wallet/credit system JWT wrong key → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_wrong_key}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-wrongkey-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.6 POST /wallet/credit system JWT expired → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_expired}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-expired-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.7 POST /wallet/credit system JWT NO exp claim → 401 (Wallet must require exp)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["// jjwt only validates exp if PRESENT. SystemTokenVerifier must explicitly","// require the exp claim — otherwise a token with no exp lives forever, and a","// leaked token has no clock-based recovery.","pm.test('401 (token without exp must be refused)',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_no_exp}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-noexp-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.8 GET /wallet/me/summary no token → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/me/summary","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","me","summary"]}}},
        {"name":"1.9 GET /wallet/me/summary expired user JWT → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_expired}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/me/summary","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","me","summary"]}}},
        {"name":"1.10 GET /wallet/me/summary wrong-key user JWT → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_wrong_key}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/me/summary","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","me","summary"]}}},
        {"name":"1.11 POST /wallet/debit missing Idempotency-Key → 400","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('400 (missing required header)',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(400));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":100,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}},
        {"name":"1.12 /admin/wallet without admin role → 403","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('403',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(403));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/admin/wallet/{{bob_user_id}}","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","admin","wallet","{{bob_user_id}}"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. /wallet/credit (system)",
      "item": [
        {"name":"2.1 credit alice 5000 BAN_REFUND → 201","event":[{"listen":"prerequest","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.environment.set('credit_idem','k-credit-{{run_stamp}}-1');"]}},{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('201',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(201));","const j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('walletEntryId returned',()=>pm.expect(j.walletEntryId).to.be.a('string'));","pm.test('newBalanceCents >= 5000',()=>pm.expect(j.newBalanceCents).to.be.at.least(5000));","pm.environment.set('alice_balance_after_2_1', j.newBalanceCents);"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"{{credit_idem}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":5000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\",\"externalRef\":\"sub-ban-{{run_stamp}}\",\"memo\":\"contract 2.1\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"2.2 replay SAME key → 200 (cached)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200 (cached replay)',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","const j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('same balance as 2.1',()=>pm.expect(j.newBalanceCents).to.eql(parseInt(pm.environment.get('alice_balance_after_2_1'))));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"{{credit_idem}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":5000,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\",\"externalRef\":\"sub-ban-{{run_stamp}}\",\"memo\":\"contract 2.1\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"2.3 replay SAME key + DIFFERENT body → 200 cached OR 409 (body-hash strict)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["// Payment had this as a finding; Wallet inherits the same pattern. If","// IdempotencyService has the body-hash strict variant we'd see 409. If not,","// we'd see 200 cached. Either is captured here so we can spot the contract.","pm.test('200 or 409',()=>pm.expect([200,409]).to.include(pm.response.code));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"{{credit_idem}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":99999,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\",\"externalRef\":\"DIFFERENT\",\"memo\":\"DIFFERENT\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"2.4 different key + different body → 201 new entry, balance grows","event":[{"listen":"prerequest","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.environment.set('credit_idem2','k-credit-{{run_stamp}}-2');"]}},{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('201',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(201));","const prev=parseInt(pm.environment.get('alice_balance_after_2_1'));","pm.test('balance grew by 1500',()=>pm.expect(pm.response.json().newBalanceCents).to.eql(prev + 1500));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"{{credit_idem2}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1500,\"source\":\"CHARGEBACK\",\"externalRef\":\"cb-{{run_stamp}}\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"2.5 invalid source enum → 400 or 422","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('400 or 422',()=>pm.expect([400,422]).to.include(pm.response.code));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-badsrc-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":100,\"source\":\"NONSENSE\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"2.6 negative amount → 400 (@Positive)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('400',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(400));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-neg-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":-100,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"2.7 zero amount → 400 (@Positive)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('400',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(400));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-zero-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":0,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}},
        {"name":"2.8 missing userId → 400","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('400',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(400));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-nouid-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"amountCents\":100,\"source\":\"BAN_REFUND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/credit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","credit"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. /wallet/debit (user)",
      "item": [
        {"name":"3.1 debit alice 200 → 201","event":[{"listen":"prerequest","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.environment.set('debit_idem','k-debit-{{run_stamp}}-1');"]}},{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('201',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(201));","const j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('walletEntryId returned',()=>pm.expect(j.walletEntryId).to.be.a('string'));","pm.environment.set('alice_balance_after_3_1', j.newBalanceCents);"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"{{debit_idem}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":200,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\",\"externalRef\":\"order-{{run_stamp}}\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}},
        {"name":"3.2 debit replay same key → 200 cached","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","pm.test('same balance',()=>pm.expect(pm.response.json().newBalanceCents).to.eql(parseInt(pm.environment.get('alice_balance_after_3_1'))));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"{{debit_idem}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":200,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\",\"externalRef\":\"order-{{run_stamp}}\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}},
        {"name":"3.3 alice tries to debit BOB → 403","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('403 (cant debit another user)',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(403));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-cross-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{bob_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":100,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}},
        {"name":"3.4 admin debits a never-credited user → 400 InsufficientBalance","event":[{"listen":"prerequest","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["// Use a per-run random user id so this assertion is independent of any","// prior test in the suite (or any prior run) that may have credited Bob.","const hex = '0123456789abcdef';","let r='00000099-0000-0000-0000-';","for(let i=0;i<12;i++) r += hex.charAt(Math.floor(Math.random()*16));","pm.environment.set('cold_user_id', r);"]}},{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["// Wallet row doesn't exist for this user. WalletService.debit returns","// 400 InsufficientBalance: Wallet not found per Wallet PDF Decision 4.1","// (400 routes Subscription's fallback to Payment).","pm.test('400 (no wallet)',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(400));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_admin}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-admindebit-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{cold_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}},
        {"name":"3.5 debit insufficient balance → 400 (Wallet PDF Decision 4.1)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["// Wallet PDF Decision 4.1 — InsufficientBalanceException maps to 400 (not 422)","// so Subscription's purchase flow can fall through to Payment in the same","// HTTP class as 'malformed request'. Deliberate design, not a bug.","pm.test('400 InsufficientBalance',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(400));","pm.test('body mentions InsufficientBalance',()=>pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('InsufficientBalance'));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-overdraft-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":99999999,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}},
        {"name":"3.6 debit negative → 400","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('400',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(400));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-negdebit-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":-50,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}},
        {"name":"3.7 debit user_jwt_no_userid → 401 or 403 (no userId claim)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["// Token has valid signature/exp/aud but lacks userId. JwtAuthenticationFilter","// silently clears the context, so principal is null in the controller. The","// controller's null-check then returns 403. Either 401 or 403 is a sensible","// outcome for 'token missing required claim'.","pm.test('401 or 403',()=>pm.expect([401,403]).to.include(pm.response.code));"]}}],"request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_no_userid}}"},{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Idempotency-Key","value":"k-nouid-{{$timestamp}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"userId\":\"{{alice_user_id}}\",\"amountCents\":1,\"source\":\"IN_APP_SPEND\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/debit","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","debit"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. /wallet/me/summary + /wallet/{userId}/summary",
      "item": [
        {"name":"4.1 alice gets own summary → 200, balance > 0","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","const j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('availableCents > 0 (alice has been credited)',()=>pm.expect(j.availableCents).to.be.above(0));","pm.test('currency = EGP',()=>pm.expect(j.currency).to.eql('EGP'));","pm.test('recentActivity is array',()=>pm.expect(j.recentActivity).to.be.an('array'));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/me/summary","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","me","summary"]}}},
        {"name":"4.2 system lookup alice's summary → 200","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","pm.test('balance matches alice from 4.1',()=>pm.expect(pm.response.json().availableCents).to.be.above(0));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/{{alice_user_id}}/summary","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","{{alice_user_id}}","summary"]}}},
        {"name":"4.3 system lookup nonexistent user → empty wallet shape","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200 or 404',()=>pm.expect([200,404]).to.include(pm.response.code));","if (pm.response.code === 200) {","  pm.test('zero balance for never-credited user',()=>pm.expect(pm.response.json().availableCents).to.eql(0));","}"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{system_jwt_service}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/summary","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","summary"]}}},
        {"name":"4.4 /wallet/{uid}/summary with user JWT (not system) → 401","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('401 (system-only endpoint)',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(401));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/{{alice_user_id}}/summary","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","{{alice_user_id}}","summary"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. /wallet/me/entries (pagination)",
      "item": [
        {"name":"5.1 default page → 200, has at least 2 entries (credit+debit so far)","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","const j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('content is array',()=>pm.expect(j.content).to.be.an('array'));","pm.test('at least one entry',()=>pm.expect(j.content.length).to.be.at.least(1));","pm.test('default size 50',()=>pm.expect(j.size).to.eql(50));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/me/entries","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","me","entries"]}}},
        {"name":"5.2 size=2 → only 2 returned","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","pm.test('at most 2 returned',()=>pm.expect(pm.response.json().content.length).to.be.at.most(2));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/me/entries?size=2","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","me","entries"],"query":[{"key":"size","value":"2"}]}}},
        {"name":"5.3 size=500 (over cap) → clamped to 200","event":[{"listen":"test","script":{"type":"text/javascript","exec":["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","pm.test('size clamped to 200',()=>pm.expect(pm.response.json().size).to.eql(200));"]}}],"request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{user_jwt_alice}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{wallet_url}}/api/wallet/me/entries?size=500","host":["{{wallet_url}}"],"path":["api","wallet","me","entries"],"query":[{"key":"size","value":"500"}]}}},
